            <title>George Elgar Hicks의 &lt;Forward she started with a happy cry&gt;란 작품을 감상하고.</title>
            <author id="P04545" age="19" occupation="직장인/전문직" sex="F" submission="온라인" handwriting="No">신지현</author>
        </sourceInfo>
